# Tiimo MCP server config — copy to .env and fill in. NEVER commit .env.
#
# ── TIIMO_SESSION_COOKIE (recommended — enables auto-refresh) ─────────────────
# The Tiimo web app authenticates with NextAuth.js. Its session cookie is a
# ~30-day ROLLING credential; with it, the MCP self-heals expired access tokens
# automatically (no more ~5-day manual token re-grabs). Capture it ONCE:
#     1. Open https://webapp.tiimoapp.com and log in (premium web app).
#     2. DevTools (Cmd+Opt+I) -> Network tab -> reload -> click the request to
#        "/api/auth/session".
#     3. Headers -> Request Headers -> copy the FULL "cookie:" header value and
#        paste it as TIIMO_SESSION_COOKIE below (one line; the whole thing is
#        fine — extra cookies are harmless, and copying all of it captures any
#        chunked "__Secure-next-auth.session-token.0/.1" pieces automatically).
#   On each refresh the MCP calls /api/auth/session with this cookie, gets a
#   fresh access token (NextAuth does the OIDC refresh server-side), and writes
#   the new token — and any rotated session cookie — back to this file.
#   If it ever expires (signed out, or idle > ~30 days), re-capture the same way.
TIIMO_SESSION_COOKIE=

# ── TIIMO_TOKEN (Bearer access token; auto-refreshed if the cookie is set) ────
#   The MCP re-reads and rewrites this live. To seed it manually (or if you skip
#   the session cookie, valid ~5 days then re-grab):
#     1. Open https://webapp.tiimoapp.com and log in.
#     2. DevTools -> Network -> filter "api.tiimoapp.com" -> click any request.
#     3. Headers -> Request Headers -> copy the "authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>"
#        value (just the <TOKEN> part).
#   It's a JWT (iss=auth.tiimoapp.com, aud=api.tiimoapp.com), ~5-day lifetime.
TIIMO_TOKEN=

# TIIMO_PROFILE_ID — your Tiimo profile UUID. Find it in the same Network tab:
#   it's the {profileId} segment in /api/profiles/{profileId}/todo-task-lists.
TIIMO_PROFILE_ID=

# Optional — defaults shown.
# TIIMO_API_BASE=https://api.tiimoapp.com/api
# TIIMO_SESSION_URL=https://webapp.tiimoapp.com/api/auth/session
